---VS Code---
-> dotnet new webapi -n CommandService
-> dotnet build
-> dotnet run
-> dotnet ef migrations add initialmigration
-> code -r <ServiceName>
---Docker---
-> docker build -t ilterstellar/platformservice .
-> docker ps
-> docker images
-> docker containers
-> docker push ilterstellar/platformservice
-> docker run -p 6060:80 -d ilterstellar/platformservice
---Kubernetes---
-> kubectl get deployments
-> kubectl get pods
-> kubectl get services
-> kubectl rollout restart deployment platforms-depl
-> kubectl apply -f platforms-depl.yaml
-> kubectl delete deployment platforms-depl
-> kubectl create secret generic mssql --from-literal=SA_PASSWORD="pa55w0rd!"
-> kubectl get pvc
-> kubectl get storage class


---Routes---
-> Local
  -> Platform http://localhost:5099/api/platforms/
  -> Command http://localhost:5144/api/c/platforms/
-> Node Port
  -> http://localhost:30780/api/platforms
-> Nginx
  -> https://acme.com/api/platforms
